visa 嘅international student 冇得報part-time, 但係bno 戈個5+1 visa 應該唔算係 tier 4 student visa<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T03:51:47.000Z","msg":"個邏輯應該係:<br />\n1) tier 4 visa冇得報part time<br />\n2) BNO visa =/= tier 4<br />\n3) 所以以上restriction咪不適用於BNO<br />\n<br />\n以我認知BNO似係自己sponsor自己嘅visa, as long as銀行存款夠多餓唔死, 就算過去退休hea都得？<br />\n遲啲應該有多啲specific guideline啦，而家啲學校都未跟得切新policy<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176e2df3f8d98d8c626b73cc8adb378832b102d7","tid":2150461,"uid":332362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T03:52:27.000Z","msg":"官綱對BNO Visa 係無任何限制 ㄧ撿就5年 可讀書/工作/Hea 第6年可自行申請入籍 詳請可自己去官網處查看。"},{"pid":"9e30f55efeecf77f6dc6be91d9482573f2084e63","tid":2150461,"uid":227891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54ac029bc2f5733dd3113a5e9466b8ef791fbbb8","tid":2150461,"uid":250550,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5e4f2f3f56f46181a20dfcee3edcb449b3183213","tid":2150461,"uid":227891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T03:14:56.000Z","msg":"我想問下有冇巴打絲打知道遲啲英國出咗5+1 visa之後有冇得喺英國讀part-time master degree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我上過啲學校網睇，佢地話如果用tier 4 visa 嘅international student 冇得報part-time, 但係bno 戈個5+1 visa 應該唔算係 tier 4 student visa<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T03:51:47.000Z","msg":"個邏輯應該係:<br />\n1) tier 4 visa冇得報part time<br />\n2) BNO visa =/= tier 4<br />\n3) 所以以上restriction咪不適用於BNO<br />\n<br />\n以我認知BNO似係自己sponsor自己嘅visa, as long as銀行存款夠多餓唔死, 就算過去退休hea都得？<br />\n遲啲應該有多啲specific guideline啦，而家啲學校都未跟得切新policy<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T03:55:31.000Z","msg":"咁你戈陣報學校係簡UK/EU? 我睇過UK/EU 個張 application form, 佢唔洗填IELTS 成績。 但係international student 應該要考IELTS<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8697b9d0808f3541d9726a94c3bf110f0c5f0bac","tid":2150461,"uid":332362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T03:55:39.000Z","msg":"Student Visa x= Working Visa x= BNO Visa"},{"pid":"ed42b139cc663697a99f59696f14693dc817c287","tid":2150461,"uid":250550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2620340f521374d3b14fd2561b6e3098b31ab82a","tid":2150461,"uid":227891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T03:50:25.000Z","msg":"之前英國嘅 international student 全部都要申請 student visa, 可能因為BNO visa 太新，所以好多學校都唔知係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T03:59:19.000Z","msg":"一係等多陣<br />\n一係直頭local student咁報，佢唔比先再negotiate/ 當special case處理<br />\nBNO &quot;citizen&quot;嘛，有可能當到local<br />\n你入境同讀書係兩件事<br />\ninternational student係入境為咗讀書，個學席係grounds for visa application<br />\n但BNO visa申請條件同你讀書無關<br />\n你咪當自己先用BNO入境移居，跟住搵世藝讀part time"},{"pid":"2953147fbb362af5eb0832ca7e3ef480073b134a","tid":2150461,"uid":227891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8697b9d0808f3541d9726a94c3bf110f0c5f0bac","tid":2150461,"uid":332362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T03:55:39.000Z","msg":"Student Visa x= Working Visa x= BNO Visa"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T04:01:39.000Z","msg":"我上學校網頁報名戈陣，一個係UK/EU，一個係international student. UK/EU戈個有得簡part time，但係international student 戈個冇得簡part time。咁我報名戈陣，應該係簡UK/EU 戈個，再寫返我ielts 成績？"},{"pid":"e26c474e80fea5dcda71fcf07d934e419c5c3683","tid":2150461,"uid":250550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e30f55efeecf77f6dc6be91d9482573f2084e63","tid":2150461,"uid":227891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc