ha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04751a6eb59f83c105b96a92f6969258fdc252e8","tid":2150461,"uid":107201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:24:33.000Z","msg":"諗緊part time定full time好啲<br />\npart time master萬一學校係山旮旯地方係咪都搵唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFull time 大拿拿250-300k又真係幾肉赤"},{"pid":"8e6e4f61701911710af620a040042f950443aa97","tid":2150461,"uid":227891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04751a6eb59f83c105b96a92f6969258fdc252e8","tid":2150461,"uid":107201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:24:33.000Z","msg":"諗緊part time定full time好啲<br />\npart time master萬一學校係山旮旯地方係咪都搵唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFull time 大拿拿250-300k又真係幾肉赤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:01:57.000Z","msg":"應該會揾到工嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大拿拿拎咁多錢出嚟又真係難啲，仲要計埋生活費，都唔知total 要一次過拎幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />窮L都係去讀part time 算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee047fd282cd95070348bbf0a35b624625bb62e","tid":2150461,"uid":332362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:55:26.000Z","msg":"BNO Visa 係未來式 咩Terms係要睇UK Immigration掂去count個身份國籍 以英人的傳統+保守 可能會𨒂續過往BNO做法 因唔洗諗 其實做得BNO Visa 都係想ㄧ條龍5+1 樓主其實應凖備過去先諗往和工作 你去到5年內 可能連博士都讀埋啦 到時生埋仔都唔會再番香港 現在應諗下去到點落腳仲實際。"},{"pid":"93cc3ae81ba3ac8431ea09e1865f5c66d0727a98","tid":2150461,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:12:10.000Z","msg":"你申唔申請到呢個Visa都唔肯定人哋點會俾你用呢個Visa報名"}]}